name: Future Pauses
description: By Travis LeRoy Southworth | @travisleroy | “Future Pauses” (2021), 2550 x 3000px. This digital painting is part of my series "Thresholds" where I create works partly through a GAN and my own computerized brush strokes. I use the word 'threshold' for my series as it can be a boundary or a starting point of an experience. They are meant to exist on the border between color field and abstract portrait. Special edition of 100 to celebrate the return of HEN on July 7th, 2021.
